des: Overpower Oceans is a weekly presentation on the most important thoughts and ideas to grow your leadership skills. These leadership development topics may surprise you and definitely will spur your thoughts on growing your leadership skills. Dont miss this chance to grow your leadership skills. Wayne Sharer is in the forefront of leadership development today with his book Overpower Oceans: 7 Leadership Principles that Crush Your Most Powerful Mental Barriers. Overpower Oceans is the First and Only Leadership Book detailing the Leadership Principles you must embrace to overcome the most powerful barriers to your leadership success. This skill takes it even deeper.
